27D057A2.Line7.541E6: We make for the hunting grounds.

59F2EB1C.Line1.541E6: Do you now? The tales walk tall ahead of you, wanderer. Tell me, are you worthy of them?

8DDBDE20.Line5.541E6: Good answer. To call yourself Oxen Tribe, you must earn it in blood, spilled in the sight of our ancestors. I will be their witness.
